biocode.fims.rest.services.rest

Class ProjectService

  • java.lang.Object
    • biocode.fims.rest.FimsService
      • biocode.fims.rest.services.rest.ProjectService

  • @Path(value="projects")
public class ProjectService
extends FimsService
    REST interface calls for working with projects. This includes fetching details associated with projects. Currently, there are no REST services for creating projects, which instead must be added to the Database manually by an administrator
